Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.36,0:01:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:68365,71535}{\i1}Although it took them\Na long time, Isabelle and Jean
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.53,0:01:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:71535,75438}{\i1}succeeded in avoiding many dangers\Nand delivered the secret letter to London.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.43,0:01:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:75438,79009}{\i1}Despite having an arrest warrant\Nlooming over them,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.00,0:01:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:79009,82712}{\i1}with Victor's help, they managed\Nto return to Versailles.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.41,0:01:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:88418,93857}{\i1}At that time in Versailles,\Nas if just waiting for them,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.85,0:01:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:93857,96993}{\i1}a rather peculiar event occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.64,0:01:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116646,118682}What a beautiful ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.68,0:02:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:118682,121518}This is my first opportunity\Nto admire such a perfect gem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:121518,125989}Oh, please. Compared to your diamond,\Nit is but a worthless pebble.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:141304,142906}What happened?\NWhat happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.90,0:02:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:142906,145609}Why did the lights go out?\NI do not like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148545,150480}Where's my necklace?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.48,0:02:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150480,152115}And the rings!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152115,153216}They're gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153483,154951}They disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.95,0:02:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154951,156720}Our jewelry is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.72,0:02:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:156720,159556}What to do?\NWhere has it gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.79,0:02:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:160790,164227}Honey, my…\NMy necklace…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164227,168131}Get a grip, Bridget.\NDon't panic over a handful of pearls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.03,0:02:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171034,172869}A picture of a bat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.83,0:03:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175839,180010}"To the people of Versailles,\Nsetting the limits of human wealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180010,184581}You have our sincere gratitude for\Nyour huge donation to our shadow army.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.18,0:03:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185181,186483}– Count Red".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188251,189719}Count Red?
