Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.44,0:24:53.45,ED EN,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1487449,1493455}Your smile is so nice
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.45,0:24:58.76,ED EN,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1493455,1498760}It displays so much love,\Ngentle like a breeze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.76,0:25:03.66,ED EN,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1498760,1503665}La la la, our song\Nreaches across the stream
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.66,0:25:08.83,ED EN,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1503665,1508837}and echoes in the green mountains
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.83,0:25:14.17,ED EN,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1508837,1514176}Let's run with all our might
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.17,0:25:20.48,ED EN,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1514176,1520482}to the top of the hill,\Nwhere our friend is
